    [ ] Main content area (renders child routes)
[ ] Set up nested routes under /dashboard:
    [ ] /dashboard/profile
    [ ] /dashboard/resume
    [ ] /dashboard/jobs
    [ ] /dashboard/history
    [ ] /dashboard/applied
    [ ] /dashboard → redirect to /dashboard/profile
[ ] Highlight active sidebar item based on current route

