    [ ] List education entries (degree, institution, years)
    [ ] "+ Add Education" button → form modal
    [ ] Edit/delete each entry
[ ] Work Experience section:
    [ ] List work experience entries (title, company, dates, description)
    [ ] "+ Add Experience" button → form modal
    [ ] Edit/delete each entry
